印度-斯基泰人的祖先被認為是源自塞迦（斯基泰人）部落。

<blockquote> “在[[新疆|新疆]]舞台上較早出現的一組印歐語系人是塞迦人（中文稱為Sai（塞））。塞迦不僅是特定國家或民族的名稱，更是一個通用稱呼；塞迦部落是早期游牧民族文化中逐漸演化的一部分，地域包括[[西伯利亞|西伯利亞]]，和從新疆到[[黑海|黑海]]中部的[[歐亞大陸|歐亞大陸]]草原。就像[[希羅多德|希羅多德]]在其作品《[[歷史|歷史]]》第4卷中所描述的斯基泰人一樣（Saka是伊朗語的說法，等同於希臘語的Scythes，許多學者一提到就用綜合的Saka-Scythian來表達），塞迦人是操[[波斯語|波斯語]]的騎馬游牧民族，他們在戰爭中運用[[馬戰車|馬戰車]]、宰殺馬匹做犧牲、並將死者埋葬在墳地或是稱為{{link-en|可根|kurgan}}的大型土墩陵墓中。”<ref>Millward (2007), p. 13.</ref></blockquote>

印度西部的塞迦人使用[[塞語|塞迦語]]（因為首度在[[塔里木盆地|塔里木盆地]]得到證實，也稱為[[于闐|于闐]]語）。<ref name="DD350">{{cite book |last1=Diringer |first1=David |title=Alphabet A Key To The History Of Mankind |date=1948 |page=350 |url=https://archive.org/details/in.ernet.dli.2015.57042/page/n351/mode/2up}}</ref>

===阿契美尼德時期（公元前6到4世紀）===
發生在公元前515年左右的{{le|阿契美尼德王朝征服印度河流域|Achaemenid conquest of the Indus Valley}}過程中，阿契美尼德軍隊並非單獨由波斯人組成，可能有塞迦人參與。阿契美尼德軍隊由遼闊帝國中不同的民族，包括巴克特里亞人、塞迦人、帕提亞人、粟特人等共同組成。<ref name="Beckwith p.5">{{cite book |last1=Beckwith |first1=Christopher I. |title=Greek Buddha: Pyrrho's Encounter with Early Buddhism in Central Asia |date=2015 |publisher=Princeton University Press |isbn=9781400866328 |page=5 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=RlCUBgAAQBAJ&pg=PA5 |language=en |access-date=2021-07-18 |archive-date=2019-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190701103139/https://books.google.com/books?id=RlCUBgAAQBAJ&pg=PA5 |dead-url=no }}</ref>希羅多德曾把不同種族的軍隊組成列出，其中包括塞迦人和[[臾那|愛奧尼亞人]]（來自希臘），甚至有[[伊索比亞|伊索比亞]]人。<ref name="Beckwith p.5">{{cite book |last1=Beckwith |first1=Christopher I. |title=Greek Buddha: Pyrrho's Encounter with Early Buddhism in Central Asia |date=2015 |publisher=Princeton University Press |isbn=9781400866328 |page=5 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=RlCUBgAAQBAJ&pg=PA5 |language=en}}</ref>這些種族的人很可能都加入阿契美尼德軍隊，一起入侵印度。<ref>Herodotus [https://penelope.uchicago.edu/Thayer/E/Roman/Texts/Herodotus/7B*.html VII 65]</ref><ref name="Beckwith p.5"/> These ethnicities are likely to have been included in the Achaemenid army which invaded India.<ref name="Beckwith p.5"/>

包括{{le|麥克·魏策爾|Michael Witzel}}<ref>{{cite book |last1=Attwood |first1=Jayarava |title=Possible Iranian Origins for the Śākyas and Aspects of Buddhism |url=https://www.academia.edu/25950011 |language=en |pages=47–69 |access-date=2021-07-18 |archive-date=2021-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210717064837/https://www.academia.edu/25950011 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[白桂思|白桂思]]<ref name="CIB">{{cite book |last1=Beckwith |first1=Christopher I. |title=Greek Buddha: Pyrrho's Encounter with Early Buddhism in Central Asia |date=2015 |publisher=Princeton University Press |isbn=9781400866328 |pages=1–21 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=RlCUBgAAQBAJ&pg=PA1 |language=en |access-date=2021-07-18 |archive-date=2020-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125093559/https://books.google.com/books?id=RlCUBgAAQBAJ&pg=PA1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在內的某些學者認為[[釋迦族|釋迦族]]，即史上[[釋迦牟尼|釋迦牟尼]]的族人，是源自中亞的斯基泰人，而印度稱為Śākya的[[民族称呼|民族称呼]]與“Scythian”起源相同，指的就是塞迦人。<ref name="Beckwith p.5"/>這也為在印度的塞迦人強力支持佛教信仰的原因提出解釋。<ref name="CIB"/>

波斯人、薩卡人、和希臘人後來可能加入[[旃陀羅笈多|旃陀羅笈多]]的征戰，在公元前320年左右奪下[[摩揭陀|摩揭陀]]王位。在公元四至八世紀寫就的[[梵語|梵語]]戲劇作品{{le|Mudrarakshasa|Mudrarakshasa}}說，在[[亞歷山大大帝|亞歷山大大帝]]死後，旃陀羅笈多動用“塞迦人-[[臾那|臾那]]人-[[劍浮沙|劍浮沙]]人-波斯人-巴克特里亞人”的聯盟軍隊，奪得摩揭陀寶座，而建立[[孔雀王朝|孔雀王朝]]。<ref name="RM">{{cite book |last1=Mookerji |first1=Radhakumud |title=Chandragupta Maurya and His Times |date=1966 |publisher=Motilal Banarsidass |isbn=9788120804050 |page=27 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=i-y6ZUheQH8C&pg=PA27 |language=en |access-date=2021-07-18 |archive-date=2020-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200531130644/https://books.google.com/books?id=i-y6ZUheQH8C&pg=PA27%2F |dead-url=no }}; {{cite book |last=Mookerji |first=Radha Kumud |chapter=The Foundation of the Mauryan Empire |editor=K. A. Nilakanta Sastri |title=A Comprehensive History of India, Volume 2: Mauryas and Satavahanas |date=1957 |publisher=Orient Longmans |page=4 |chapter-url=https://archive.org/details/in.ernet.dli.2015.532644/page/n5 }}: "The Mudrarakshasa further informs us that his Himalayan alliance gave Chandragupta a composite army ... Among these are mentioned the following : Sakas, Yavanas (probably Greeks), Kiratas, Kambojas, Parasikas and Bahlikas."</ref><ref name="DS">{{cite journal |author=D. B. Spooner |year=1915 |title=The Zoroastrian Period of Indian History |journal=[[Journal_of_the_Royal_Asiatic_Society_of_Great_Britain_and_Ireland|Journal of the Royal Asiatic Society of Great Britain and Ireland]] |volume=47 |issue=3 |pages=416–417 |doi=10.1017/S0035869X00048437 |jstor=25189338 |url=https://zenodo.org/record/2403053 |access-date=2021-07-18 |archive-date=2021-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210719091245/https://zenodo.org/record/2403053 |dead-url=no }}: "After Alexander's death, when Chandragupta marched on [[Magadha|Magada]], it was with largely the Persian army that he won the throne of India. The testimony of the [[Mudrarakshasa|Mudrarakshasa]] is explicit on this point, and we have no reason to doubt its accuracy in matter[s] of this kind."</ref><ref name="EI134">{{cite book |last1=Shashi |first1=Shyam Singh |title=Encyclopaedia Indica: Mauryas |date=1999 |publisher=Anmol Publications |isbn=9788170418597 |page=134 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=HfwvAQAAIAAJ |language=en |access-date=2021-07-18 |archive-date=2020-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200531130644/https://books.google.com/books?id=HfwvAQAAIAAJ%2F |dead-url=no }}: "Among those who helped Chandragupta in his struggle against the Nandas, were the Sakas (Scythians), Yavanas (Greeks), and Parasikas (Persians)"</ref><ref>{{cite book |last1=Mookerji |first1=Radhakumud |title=Chandragupta Maurya and His Times |date=1966 |publisher=Motilal Banarsidass |isbn=9788120804050 |page=210 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=i-y6ZUheQH8C&pg=PA210 |language=en |access-date=2021-07-18 |archive-date=2020-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200531124118/https://books.google.com/books?id=i-y6ZUheQH8C&pg=PA210 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===月氏擴張（公元前第2世紀）===
在公元前2世紀，中亞[[游牧民族|游牧]]部落之中開始新的遷徙。此事件在[[漢朝|漢朝]]和其他中國史書中都有記載，這種龐大的部落遷徙始於[[月氏|月氏]]部落被匈奴擊敗，向西逃亡，並在西向移居過程中，引發其他中亞部落也被迫遷移的[[多米諾骨牌效應|多米諾骨牌效應]]。<ref name=Rene>{{Cite book |last=Grousset |first=Rene |title=The Empire of the Steppes |publisher=Rutgers University Press |year=1970 |isbn=978-0-8135-1304-1 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/empireofsteppesh00prof/page/32 32] |url=https://archive.org/details/empireofsteppesh00prof/page/32 }}</ref>
[[File:Orlat_plaque_detail.jpg|thumb]]
 
根據這些古老的資料，來自[[蒙古|蒙古]]的匈奴[[冒頓|冒頓]]單于襲擊月氏（月氏人可能與居住在塔里木盆地東部的[[吐火羅人|吐火羅人]]有關），並在公元前175年左右將其從位於[[祁連山|祁連山]]和[[敦煌|敦煌]]之間的家園驅離。<ref>''Shiji'', chap. 123 translated in: Burton Watson (1993), p. 234.</ref>大多數月氏人向西遷移到[[伊犁河|伊犁河]]地區，少數人留下。他們讓居住在伊犁河地區的塞迦人流離失所，塞迦人被迫向南遷移到[[費爾干納|費爾干納]]和粟特。根據中國歷史編年史資料（[[塞迦|塞迦]]人被稱為“ Sai”塞人）：“月氏襲擊塞族國王，後者向南遷徙甚遠，他們原有的土地為月氏人佔領。”<ref>''[[Hanshu|Han Shu]]'' 61 4B Original tex: 西擊塞王。塞王南走遠徙，月氏居其地。</ref><ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.transoxiana.org/Eran/Articles/benjamin.html |title=The Yuezhi Migration and Sogdia |author=Craig Benjamin |journal=Transoxiana Webfestschrift Series I: Eran Ud Aneran |date=October 2003 |access-date=2019-12-22 |archive-date=2015-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150218204941/http://www.transoxiana.org/Eran/Articles/benjamin.html |url-status=yes }}</ref>

約在公元前155年之後，月氏再次被[[烏孫|烏孫]]和匈奴聯盟所擊敗，被迫再向南移動，而又再次驅散斯基泰人，後者向南遷移至巴克特里亞和今日的[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]，並向西南方向的[[帕提亞|帕提亞]]接近。公元前145年左右，塞迦人似乎已進入[[希臘-巴克特里亞王國|希臘-巴克特里亞王國]]的領土，他們在那裡把希臘城市{{link-en|埃康農|Alexandria on the Oxus}}焚為為平地。（請參閱[[希臘-巴克特里亞王國|希臘-巴克特里亞王國]]#滅亡）月氏留在[[阿姆河|阿姆河]]北岸的粟特，但正如中國漢朝使者[[張騫|張騫]]在公元前126年訪問該地區時所描述，他們成為巴克特里亞地區塞迦人的宗主國。<ref>{{cite web
